{"tid":1225441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家已經開始鬆懈","createTime":"2019-06-15T07:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T21:02:35.000Z","uid":74642,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc916cdbcbf86fe0d9596a1bdc05e75adf868cb","tid":1225441,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"今日一宣布暫緩，相信大家身邊的親戚朋友一定有部分會聽日因此唔企出黎<br />\n而身邊的話題亦都開始多返，吹水台亦出現返其他唔同類型的post，無左早幾日洗板推post，團結一致的氣氛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">好想大家都出一分力，同你身邊嘅屋企人，朋友講，聽日一定要出嚟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁難得嚟到呢步，之前d長輩都覺得我地做咩都好，冇可能改變到啲咩，今次有少少成果，但唔好就咁收貨，我地更應該乘勝追擊，堅持到底！<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好令一眾義士嘅付出付諸流水</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人，616站出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d2d86cfd3d4e7db7231db37b13ec04a529b9e768","tid":1225441,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044dee9971b8b07bfa52fba829833dc2f3f9e5b3","tid":1225441,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不設時限即係7月後再黎過<br />\n堅決爭取撤回先收貨"},{"pid":"d015ae1d305e7b59f88875b8fb016515fce0999d","tid":1225441,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:46:53.000Z","m